title: Can anyone gift me the SKT T1 Jax skin?
body:
I have decided to main Jax top and would really like a skin for him. He is my favorite champion but I cant buy the skin because I can't get RP because I don't have any money to spend. If anybody can gift me this skin I would be very happy. Please help me before the skins go back into the legacy vault.

My IGN is:  S4BRE
Please Add Me if you can help. Thanks.

{{champion:24}}
